 from a point of view close to my own. He has some Russian background. He has taught, I am told, at the N.Y.U. and the New School (Shakespeare and writing courses) and has recommendations from both. His address is 47 Perry Street, New York 14, NY.





TO: PYKE JOHNSON, JR.1

CC, 1 p.





Goldwin Smith Hall

Ithaca, NY.

December 16, 1958

